Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.36,0:00:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞逝的秒针 闪耀的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现代社会中衰竭的心灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.74,0:00:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一贴良药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.74,0:00:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是隐藏在绑架背后的惊人秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看穿唯一的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 头脑则是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.16,0:01:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩踢罐子的元太 光彦 步美和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.18,0:01:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人气组合[TWO-MIX]的主唱 高山美奈美小姐到餐厅吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.62,0:01:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高山小姐为了寻找联系不上的永野椎菜先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.11,0:01:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而从演唱会现场跑了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在那个餐厅里……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.75,0:02:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高山小姐在我们的眼前被绑架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.15,0:02:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人要的是她忘在餐厅里的包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.37,0:02:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还叫我们少年侦探团送去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.49,0:02:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来犯人想要的是[TWO-MIX]的练习录音带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.39,0:02:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照要求运送包的我们 接到犯人的联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.40,0:02:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人叫我们甩开跟随的警察 让步美一个人送去练习录音带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让步美一个人去做这么危险的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.22,0:02:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时我想到个主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.89,0:02:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好小妹妹 你终于来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.76,0:02:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围应该没条子了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.72,0:03:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 做的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.99,0:03:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你能够照叔叔说的过来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美会努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.36,0:03:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.36,0:03:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人气歌手绑架事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.87,0:03:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 柯南和步美调换了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的目标是练习录音带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.86,0:03:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为犯人叫我们甩开警察让步美把录音带送去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南就代替我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.04,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么不告诉我们你们调换了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.20,0:03:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让犯人以为自己得逞了不就可以使犯人出现大意吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.79,0:03:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以柯南说在这之前我们调换的事不能被知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.09,0:03:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样一来就无法找到犯人所在地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.51,0:03:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南也会有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要使用这副追踪眼镜的话……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话功劳就全都变成柯南的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.40,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们找到犯人的老窝后再通知警察也不迟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.28,0:04:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后救出[TWO-MIX]的我们就……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们 小朋友们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.89,0:04:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都多亏了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.57,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 由我们少年侦探团去抓住犯人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么叫那么大声啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.33,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是……肚子饿了……对吧……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.15,0:04:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对……我们是在说肚子饿了……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们去买点吃的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要马上就回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.74,0:04:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了 肚子饿了 肚子饿了 ……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.93,0:05:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.77,0:05:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是按照约定一个人来的呢 小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.73,0:05:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把录音带送到从那里可以看到的仓库二楼来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最喜欢的[TWO-MIX]正等着你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来你们的用处就没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.25,0:05:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要祈祷就趁现在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿来了 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢你了小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.79,0:05:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐厅里的家伙不在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去什么地方了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.11,0:05:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.84,0:05:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要先联系警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有电话亭哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.67,0:06:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,119
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 元太 那是消防局啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.65,0:06:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报警是110
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.92,0:06:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且应该要先按下这个按钮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.30,0:06:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这里是110
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 请找目暮警部……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小朋友你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.88,0:06:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.57,0:06:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们叫我送这盘录音带来这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来 他们一直在问录音带在哪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么要找练习录音带呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.86,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之详细情况等从这里逃出去后再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察也快来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.82,0:06:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该正利用追踪眼镜往这里赶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追踪着这个发信器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.55,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你……你究竟是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.73,0:07:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户川柯南 是个侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.71,0:07:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.29,0:07:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.18,0:07:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点吧 趁另一个犯人还没回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.38,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追踪眼镜就是这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.01,0:07:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.03,0:07:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.40,0:07:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们在这附近转悠 就把他们抓来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.69,0:07:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 为什么不把眼镜交给警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.66,0:07:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要起内讧就尽管起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.75,0:07:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是在另一个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.73,0:07:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.88,0:07:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起烧成黑碳吧 你们得感谢我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.92,0:08:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 至少告诉我们为什么被绑架吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到另一个世界去问释迦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.95,0:08:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒计时的钟声响起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我转换心情跑出来后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就听到 一声两声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹如不合时节的烟火般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人在某处宣告开始的钟声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这是[TWO-MIX]的练习录音带的歌词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.85,0:08:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你绑架[TWO-MIX]的动机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说错吧 宫原悟史先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.36,0:08:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在去年的除夕夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在[升圆寺]附近杀死一名身份不明的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.44,0:08:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾接受过目暮警部的审问吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年的除夕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[升圆寺]？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.83,0:08:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里不正是我们想到这首歌的地方吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.30,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在除夕钟声响起的11点50分左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个寺院的附近发生了杀人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.75,0:09:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到这个男人报警后赶到的警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.94,0:09:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从握着手枪的死者手上查出了硝烟反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再根据弹匣里的空弹壳只有一个发来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就相信了这个人所说的 被持有手枪的精神病人袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.79,0:09:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在争执之中手枪走火的证词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次事件就被当成是正当防卫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实并不是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.68,0:09:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把手枪一开始就是你准备杀那个男子带去的手枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你第一枪射穿那个男人的心脏后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.41,0:09:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同一弹匣里装上子弹 朝地面开枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.61,0:09:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让他的手上留有硝烟反应而让他握着手枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近也没有目击者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你去向警察报警的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.46,0:09:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剩下的子弹和弹壳交给在门口睡觉的男的带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来这一切都很顺利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是有人……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了那个声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那难道是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们[TWO-MIX]的俩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒计时的钟声是除夕夜的钟声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两声烟火声就是两声枪响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.23,0:10:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及在歌词开头的[跨越了1996]说明时间是1996年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.24,0:10:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些加上[TWO-MIX]在电台里说的[升圆寺]的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.50,0:10:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能知道两声枪响的时间和地点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.87,0:10:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也听了吧 播放了练习录音带的那次广播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才绑架了[TWO-MIX]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在警察察觉之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们俩个和录音带一起抹杀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还挺聪明的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是宫原悟史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.40,0:10:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我杀死的是以前我们抢银行时的同伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.19,0:11:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然回来威胁说要向警察供出一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.53,0:11:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.29,0:11:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你那时逃跑的话 不是就找不到你了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.45,0:11:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法啊 因为被人看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.89,0:11:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我去和他见面的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸被寺院的和尚看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好那个和尚的耳朵不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就他一个人要留在寺院里敲钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就放了他一条生路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想听了那枪声后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.01,0:11:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会有人拿去写成歌曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.21,0:11:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动手机吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我交给在那边的搭档的电话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.08,0:11:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不能掉以轻心的小鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算现在把警察叫来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.76,0:11:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕在赶来救你们之前 你们就已经被烧死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢慢地享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.20,0:12:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是目暮警部吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.95,0:12:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经平安地把他们俩个和那些孩子放回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.81,0:12:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.14,0:12:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.59,0:12:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没提柯南他们调换的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.36,0:12:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才无线电里联系说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.37,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小孩子的声音打电话到110找目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.69,0:12:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 是什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约在15分钟之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早点说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是……因为没说是什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.00,0:12:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当班的人以为那只是恶作剧……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道地点是哪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.05,0:12:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为时间太短 所以无法进行逆向追踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.39,0:12:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一那个电话是被犯人挂断的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 纹丝不动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 用脚力增强鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.66,0:13:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.47,0:13:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 果然不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.14,0:13:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友你们不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话大家就都没救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吸到烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把身体再放低些……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 就会给我添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.48,0:13:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些条子真烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我适可而……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早就出来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.97,0:13:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在是从警察局打的电话哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不信的话你回去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.88,0:14:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.20,0:14:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 很有用吧 这个耳环型行动电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.73,0:14:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了快点吧 现在还赶的上演唱会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.55,0:14:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.23,0:14:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.83,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎 椎菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些小鬼可别小看我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你们一个一个打死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈美姐姐好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.12,0:15:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈美姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.66,0:15:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算赶上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟后 消防车和巡逻车赶到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.38,0:15:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俩个犯人落入法网
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.90,0:15:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我们少年侦探团被狠训了一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为我们救出了高山美奈美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是被[无罪释放]了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后坐目暮警部的巡逻车直奔武道馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在搞什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经延迟30分钟了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.96,0:15:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不秒啊 客人开始骚动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.73,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们要去换衣服 你们到舞台后面等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.94,0:16:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台后面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一会我想把你们介绍给大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.67,0:16:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给大家……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈美还没来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 在搞什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 这里是舞台后面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.48,0:16:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不能随便进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.44,0:16:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回到自己的座位上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是高山小姐叫我们来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.22,0:16:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈美来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 准备OP的卡拉OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁到后台去问一下还要多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.18,0:16:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.88,0:16:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.75,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.16,0:16:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯熄掉了……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 曲子放出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.15,0:17:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 美奈美他们还没来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把曲子停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.03,0:17:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 现在停下的话可就没刚才的骚动那么简单了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.66,0:17:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.83,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正在想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 有这首歌的歌词吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.25,0:17:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要歌词的话 就在那边的CD盒子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.29,0:17:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿那个到底要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.73,0:18:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个歌声……我好象在哪听过……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.02,0:18:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别开这么可怕的玩笑嘛……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.76,0:18:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在唱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.87,0:18:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音痴的好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但声音是高山的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.58,0:18:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很难听吗……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.21,0:18:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.20,0:19:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样在我们少年侦探团的乱入下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.54,0:20:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[TWO-MIX]的武道馆现场演唱会 总算平安结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.89,0:20:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.09,0:20:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.82,0:20:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样 在舞台上演唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.34,0:20:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次也没问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 只要唱过一次就会上瘾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的侦探觉得怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是演唱会的感想呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉还算是过的去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.03,0:20:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口气不小嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.98,0:20:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是[TWO-MIX]的后台吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部先生 有事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经很累了我们还来打扰真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.28,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想问一下能不能请你们来局里做一下笔录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.67,0:21:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样呀 请稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不急 你请慢慢来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.05,0:21:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场演唱会真是很棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.31,0:21:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.24,0:21:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.64,0:21:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今天你们救了我们的谢礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家后要练习哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.68,0:21:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部先生 你们也请收下
